		{"id":"c9311a7e2c8f5752","type":"file","file":"Extras/Attachments/4444_transparent.png","x":680,"y":-1280,"width":400,"height":286},
		{
			"id":"ai_products",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 🛠️ 推荐AI产品\n\n**核心工具：**\n- ChatGPT 4.0\n- Kimi.ai（长文档处理）\n- Perplexity（AI搜索）\n- 沉浸式翻译\n\n**特色功能：**\n- 多模态能力\n- 实时总结\n- 智能搜索",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#fff3e0","borderColor":"#e65100"},
			"x":871,
			"y":-127,
			"width":350,
			"height":200
		},
		{"id":"493683880744a0f6","type":"file","file":"Extras/Attachments/3333_transparent.png","x":1120,"y":-1280,"width":400,"height":286},
		{
			"id":"kimi_demo",
			"type":"link",
