		},
		{
			"id":"learning_resources",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 📖 AI学习资源\n\n**入门资源：**\n- ChatGPT从0到1（李佳芮）\n- AIGC个人生存指南\n- 通往AGI之路\n\n**进阶内容：**\n- YouTube教程\n- B站视频课程\n- 实践案例分享",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#f1f8e9","borderColor":"#33691e"},
			"x":575,
			"y":585,
			"width":350,
			"height":180
		},
		{"id":"e3e0313ee2a3dfb2","type":"file","file":"Extras/Attachments/55555_transparent.png","x":1560,"y":-1280,"width":400,"height":286},
		{"id":"5f43166156ed6b7f","type":"file","file":"Extras/Attachments/22222_transparent.png","x":2000,"y":-1280,"width":400,"height":286},
		{
			"id":"introduction",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 🎤 引言\n\n**演讲者背景：**\n- 华为云运维工程师\n- 映兔运维工程师\n- AI工程师 → Prompts提示词工程师\n\n**核心观点：** AI能为各岗位带来效率提升",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#f3e5f5","borderColor":"#4a148c"},
			"x":-399,
			"y":-564,
			"width":500,
			"height":278
		},
		{"id":"outline","type":"text","text":"### 📋 大纲\n\n- ChatGPT 10x效率提升\n- AI产品推荐\n- 使用原则\n- 基本原理\n- 程序员姿势\n- 学习资源","x":-750,"y":-857,"width":500,"height":257},
		{
			"id":"llm_principles",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 🧠 LLM基本原理\n\n**核心机制：**\nContext上下文 + Prompts提示词 = Inference推理结果\n\n**关键概念：**\n- Token生成过程\n- 概率预测原理\n- RAG检索增强\n- Function Calling\n\n**技术本质：** 字一个字蹦出是因为对下一个字的概率预测",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#f3e5f5","borderColor":"#4a148c"},
			"x":-774,
			"y":180,
			"width":350,
			"height":200
		},
		{
			"id":"ai_principles",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 📚 AI使用原则\n\n**核心原则：**\n- 理解AI边界\n- 善用提示词\n- 多轮对话优化\n- 结合实际场景\n\n**最佳实践：**\n- 从简单问题开始\n- 逐步深入复杂任务\n- 持续学习和适应",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#fce4ec","borderColor":"#880e4f"},
			"x":-1506,
			"y":-101,
			"width":350,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"efficiency_boost",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### ⚡ ChatGPT 10x效率提升\n\n**核心对比：**\n- 常规工作流 vs AI赋能工作流\n- Prompts提示词的重要性\n- AI搜索 vs 传统搜索\n\n**关键洞见：** AI不仅是工具，更是思维方式的转变",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#e8f5e8","borderColor":"#1b5e20"},
			"x":395,
			"y":-127,
			"width":400,
			"height":200
		},
		{"id":"d90f5c4b39005f6f","type":"file","file":"Extras/Attachments/11111_transparent.png","x":220,"y":-1280,"width":400,"height":286},
		{
			"id":"programmer_tools",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 👨‍💻 程序员AI姿势\n\n**核心工具：**\n- Cursor（代码生成）\n- GitHub Copilot（代码补全）\n- ChatGPT（复杂任务）\n- Warp App（终端AI）\n\n**理念转变：**\n从 \"Talk is cheap, show me the code\"\n到 \"Code is cheap, show me your prompts\"",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#e3f2fd","borderColor":"#0d47a1"},
			"x":220,
			"y":220,
			"width":400,
			"height":180
		},
		{
			"id":"chatgpt_summary",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### 🤖 ChatGPT全文总结\n\n**会议核心要点：**\n1. AI会议纪要自动化\n2. 多模态能力展示\n3. 创意规划辅助\n4. 智能搜索与翻译\n5. 学习使用建议\n\n**关键洞见：** AI已成基础设施，人人可用自然语言编程",
			"style":{"backgroundColor":"#fff8e1","borderColor":"#f57f17"},
			"x":0,
			"y":600,
			"width":500,
			"height":150
		}
	],
